    <p>Guests can tuck into tostadas such as Tuna & Chipo­tle Mayo, Shrimps & Cholula, and freshly made wood-fired piz­zas such asTruf­fata & Bur­rata Pizza, which are made with long fer­mented dough and topped with truf­fle and mush­room paste, moz­zarella and bur­rata. All piz­zas are made with fresh dough and pre­mium in­gre­di­ents and cooked us­ing wood fire. The restau­rant also of­fers a se­lec­tion of nat­u­ral wines, beers and ciders. Also avail­able for take­aways and de­liv­ery (via www.raf­fles­gra­bandgo.com).</p>
    <p>WHERE: Butcher’s Block, Raf­fles Ar­cade, 328 North Bridge Road</p>
    <p>MRT: City Hall WHEN: Sat & Sun, noon - 2.30pm for dine-in (reg­u­lar a la carte din­ner menu & carte blanche are not avail­able for week­end lunch) PRICE: From $18 for pizza TEL: 6412-1816</p>
    <p>INFO: www.raf­fles­gra­bandgo.com/ butch­ers-block</p>


